quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  27,45,"Nokorε nso sε Yεsomaa Samuudfoͻ nua Soalhu maa no kͻͻ wͻn hͻ sε (ͻnkͻka nkyerε wͻn) sε: “Monsom mo Wura Nyankopͻn“. Na hwε, wͻbεyεε akuo mmienu a wͻreko tia wͻn ho."
  27,46,"(Soalhu) kaa sε: ”Me nkorͻfoͻ, adεn nti na morepere mo ho de bͻne adi papa anim kan? Adεn nti na monsrε Nyankopͻn hͻ bͻnefakyε sεdeε ebia yεbɛhu mo mmͻbͻ?”"
  27,47,"Wͻkaa sε: “Wo ne wͻn a wͻka wo ho no yε mmusuo ma yεn“. Soalhu kaa sε: ”Mo mmusuo no fri Nyankopͻn hͻ; daabi, moyε nnipa a mowͻ nsͻhwε mu “."
  27,48,"Na mmarima nkron bi wͻ kuro no mu a wͻdi nsεmmͻne wͻ asaase no so a wͻnyε ntotoeε pa."
  27,49,"Wͻnkaa sε: “Monfa Nyankopͻn nni nse nkyerε moho-moho sε, yεbεkͻ akͻto ahyε Soalhu ne n’abusuafoͻ so anadwo, na yɛaka akyerε ne nkorͻfoͻ sε: “Yɛnnim ͻne n’abusuafoͻ wuo no ho hwee, na nokorε na yεreka no“."
  27,50,"Enti wͻbͻͻ pͻ paa, na Yεn nso Yεbͻͻ pͻ paa wͻ aberε a na wͻnnim."
  27,51,"Enti hwε sεdeε wͻn pͻbͻͻ no awieε si wieε! Nokorε, Yεsεee wͻn ne wͻn nkorͻfoͻ no nyinaa pasaa."
  27,52,"Sεdeε wͻn afie si yͻeε no-, adane amanfoo, εnam wͻn bͻne nti. Nokorε sε nsεnkyerεnee wͻ woi mu de ma amanfoͻ a wͻnim."
  27,53,"Yεgyee wͻn a wͻgye diiε no a na wͻsuro Nyame no nkwa."
  27,54,"Lut nso, εberε a ͻka kyerεε ne nkorͻfoͻ no sε: “Adεn, morebɔ bra bͻne wͻ aberε a mo ani tua?"
  27,55,"Mofri mmaa no akyi de akͻnnͻ kͻ mmarima so? Daabi, moyε amanfoͻ bi a mo adwen awuo."
